{"id": 880, "genre": 1001, "title": "你都为你的“瘾”做过哪些事儿？", "description": "一天5杯咖啡，睡前一点小酒，打开朋友圈200次（题图来自：Ryo Takemasa）", "record_count": 6649, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607021837195PHpktjWMoXTL1bI.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-03-18T11:01:41Z", "options": [{"id": 59392, "content": "减肥上瘾……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179124}, {"id": 59393, "content": "喝珍珠奶茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 424940}, {"id": 60161, "content": "每天固定想跟一个人说话，这个人还总是各种不想理你！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462641}, {"id": 61441, "content": "失去她三年了，每天为她打一架飞机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 434925}, {"id": 59394, "content": "看手机几百次", "image": null, "praise_count": 329, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493220}, {"id": 59650, "content": "早上六点潜意识微信有人找我，在床上乱摸打开看一眼并没有…睡到十点起来再看一次…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517168}, {"id": 62466, "content": "洗澡前一定要撒泡尿！哪怕没有，也要憋出来几滴！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539185}, {"id": 59395, "content": "看剧综合症", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443759}, {"id": 59651, "content": "半夜散着头发出去买零食。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 506554}, {"id": 59396, "content": "每天去点开他的朋友圈或是微博主页", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166619}, {"id": 59397, "content": "刷剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519691}, {"id": 59653, "content": "要瘦到49kg", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522377}, {"id": 59909, "content": "挖鼻屎", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524425}, {"id": 59398, "content": "扣鼻屎………………", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 59399, "content": "每天骑行上班", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142803}, {"id": 64263, "content": "你们说的都对 我无话可说", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161457hVB9yF5d6mXNxnto.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 549797}, {"id": 59400, "content": "只和咖啡不喝水 特别是在办公室里", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 502682}, {"id": 64264, "content": "你们说的都对 我无话可说...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 549797}, {"id": 59401, "content": "下各种软件，16G手机，下完删，然后再下，用流量下载软件", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519318}, {"id": 59657, "content": "睡前等那个ta发来晚安", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 521077}, {"id": 59402, "content": "微博就算要退出了，也会在刷新一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519318}, {"id": 59658, "content": "每天必吃小零食", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473866}, {"id": 59403, "content": "ASMR!", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493335}, {"id": 59659, "content": "只要没事就刷朋友圈", "image": "img/option/option/2016060614492961Hk5bteY0c2hZ3D.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484145}, {"id": 59404, "content": "双击home键，划掉打开过的应用，即使没有打开过任何一个应用，打开手机就要点两下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 128, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365838}, {"id": 59660, "content": "每天都会登贴吧逛一圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519699}, {"id": 59405, "content": "喝奶茶喝小茗同学！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 517174}, {"id": 59661, "content": "花钱", "image": "img/option/option/20160606144928aW4ZzFhCXBxHj1Tg.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 518111}, {"id": 59918, "content": "睡前，醒来，必刷手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 230672}, {"id": 59919, "content": "看到美女就想意淫手淫人家", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 523342}, {"id": 59409, "content": "看球⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 490674}, {"id": 59665, "content": "只要看了的电视剧再没意思也坚持看完", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522659}, {"id": 59410, "content": "起床前，躺在床上刷手機1小時", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 513165}, {"id": 59411, "content": "每天翻3遍男神朋友圈 虽然他总不发新的照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 59412, "content": "跳舞上瘾，跑步上瘾，迟到上瘾", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461068}, {"id": 59669, "content": "网站签到强迫症算不算", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 65552}, {"id": 59414, "content": "不自觉地打开手机 然后发现不知道要干什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 302, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 480705}, {"id": 59415, "content": " 吃太多！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 4867}, {"id": 59416, "content": "每半小時擦护唇膏", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485485}, {"id": 60440, "content": "每年春节必买耳机，或者关于音乐的东西。持续五年了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527499}, {"id": 59417, "content": "睡前看书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 510108}, {"id": 59673, "content": "吃薯片一发不可收拾", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522734}, {"id": 59674, "content": "可乐上瘾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 181629}, {"id": 59419, "content": "吃吃吃  手机必握在手里", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 521099}, {"id": 59421, "content": "dota2", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 100669}, {"id": 59677, "content": "必12点后睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 511253}, {"id": 59933, "content": "睡前锻炼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 524599}, {"id": 59678, "content": "衣服明天再洗", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522778}, {"id": 59423, "content": "每天清各种app缓存，扫一遍所有app，斟酌还有哪个能删…#16G用户的日常#怎么可能有瘾，还不是被逼的#", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161457GQncvZ43DXE6BAUR.jpg", "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 72472}, {"id": 59679, "content": "不断地买红酒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 522780}]}